<topic id='attribute_organisation_site_code.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Attribute: ORGANISATION SITE CODE - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_organisation_site_code">ORGANISATION SITE CODE</xref>
 is a code which identifies an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation_site">ORGANISATION SITE</xref>
 uniquely.        </p>
    <p>
Note: Only 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_organisation_site_code">ORGANISATION SITE CODES</xref>
 which have been notified to and issued by the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>
 may be used.        </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>
        <p>
 codes can be downloaded from 
                          <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_technology_reference_data_update_distribution__trud_">Technology Reference Data Update Distribution (TRUD)</xref>
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>
        <p>
contact details can be found at 
                          <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_contact_details">Contact Details</xref>.                </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      <b>
All NHS 
                  <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation_site">ORGANISATION SITES</xref>
 are coded using coding frames, as shown in the tables at: 
                  <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_site_coding_frames">Organisation Site Coding Frames</xref>.            </b>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
